Write a program which prints small/large/equal relation of given two integers a and b.

import java.util.Scanner;
class Main{
public static void main(String [] args){
Scanner ip=new Scanner(System.in);
int frst=ip.nextInt();
int scnd=ip.nextInt();
if (frst < scnd){
System.out.println("a < b");}
else if( frst > scnd){
System.out.println("a > b");}
else{
System.out.println("a == b");}
}
}
